Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.66,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.74,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,We have pork miso soup and vegetable soup over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.00,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,We have rice balls too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.16,Default,ossan,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.80,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,It's fresh and hot, so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:16.48,Default,ossan,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:17.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:19.44,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The next batch of minestrone soup is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.56,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Man, there sure are a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's still pretty early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:29.66,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I think they were all waiting eagerly for some hot food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,They haven't finished restoring the infrastructure in this district yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.50,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Ah, that reminds me, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,That's your portion, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:40.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh, did you make these, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.70,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:45.74,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:46.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Thanks, Himeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.48,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I don't have much of an appetite...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.14,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Umm... How do they taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're unexpectedly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.36,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.08,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Umm... Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.26,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:08.56,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,Onii-san and Yukina-chan, thanks for helping out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.88,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,No problem, I had fun helping out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:11.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:16.06,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Besides, we're partly to blame for the destruction this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.48,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:21.60,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,I thought that we should probably get ready to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.60,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,So I came to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.22,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Right then, let's get ready and go to school-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.74,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,About that, umm... Onii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.88,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,If you'd like, please eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.08,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Umm... Kanase, did you make these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.08,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.18,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,T-Thanks, Kanase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:47.38,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I was feeling a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I-It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.46,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I could eat these all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:57.60,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,Please, eat as many as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.94,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kojou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.18,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,We'll be late for school if we don't leave soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:05.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:09.84,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I was sure you'd be hungry, so I set these aside for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.12,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.92,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,The Tartaros-Rose incident caused major damage to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.48,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,Restoration is being carried out at a fervent pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:25.22,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,but in such a situation, the one who is attracting the most attention in Itogami Island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.02,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,That's right. It is this person, Aiba Asagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.72,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,She stopped the hacking attack by the terrorist organization, Tartaros Lapus,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:38.20,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,and kept the damage to a minimum, the beautiful genius hacker, nicknamed the Digital Empress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.84,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Aiba-senpai is amazing, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.24,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,She became popular in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.78,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:49.14,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,She's been absent from school all this time because she has to help with the restoration...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:56.77,Default,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,126)}Charity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:56.77,Default,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,280)}Island Administration
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:56.77,Default,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,388)}Large-scale Restoration Project
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.36,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,She is currently very busy participating in charities for the victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:57.02,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,and the Island Administration's large-scale restoration plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:01.86,Default,Newscaster,0,0,0,,Unbelievably, she is slated to release a song supporting the restoration of Itogami Island next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A song!? By Asagi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Everyone, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:10.32,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Save Our Sanctuary, by Aiba Asagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.78,Default,SONG,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is going to be just fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.44,Default,SONG,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm here for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.50,Default,SONG,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to protect it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.22,Default,SONG,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our perfect sanctuary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.20,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.50,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Amazing! Isn't Asagi-chan amazing, Kojou-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.46,Default,SONG,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}There are things I can do,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.92,Default,SONG,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}only because I am a girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:43.78,Default,SONG,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'll cheer you on while you're doing your best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.84,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.98,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.54,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Don't you think Asagi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.60,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Isn't she different from usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.24,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.62,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,That's a fake, made using CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.04,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A fake!? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:05:59.98,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Her earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.46,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:04.80,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,There's no way Asagi would take those off, let alone wear something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:08.96,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,And besides, they're hiding it well, but she can't hold a tune to save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:09.98,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:14.38,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Seriously, Akatsuki-kun. I can't tell if you're slow or sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:18.20,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,You should pay that much attention to Asagi all the time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh? I do, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.30,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:26.36,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Geez, I don't get why Asagi's been after someone like this for all these years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.24,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:32.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Anyways, if that was CG, then the Island Administration is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why are they taking the effort to make her do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.28,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Probably because the restoration is making barely any progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:42.14,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,They're using her as they please to distract the populace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:45.50,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,"A genius hacker and high school girl protects the island."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.64,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,That's perfect material to make her popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.06,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,And she has the looks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.90,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Asagi is a beauty, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:52.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I guess she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.72,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,Don't sound so unsure about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.66,Default,Orin,0,0,0,,You blockheaded brutish devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.18,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.96,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,That Aiba-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:06.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's not like we have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:13.24,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But Senpai, you haven't met Aiba-senpai even once after the Tartaros Rose vanished, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.64,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Her phone keeps going to the answering machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:19.78,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,but she sent messages once in a while, so I wasn't worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.78,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It would be good if you could speak to her directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.76,Default,announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The monorail will be arriving shortly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:30.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll ask Yaze for advice when I go to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,He might know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:34.94,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:42.84,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,Oh, are you one of Yaze-kun's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. When was he released from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.80,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,He was moved to a different hospital, not released.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.30,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,His brother stopped by last night to pick him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Eh? Do you know where he was moved to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.36,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.94,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,Even if I did, I couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.32,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,He was moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.74,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Without saying anything to Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:05.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.46,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,How are you doing, Motoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.54,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Whats the deal, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.94,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Why did you bring me all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.78,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,For security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.24,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,I didn't think we could protect you properly in a normal hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:29.46,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Who the hell would target someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.28,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,You're going to take over as the Yaze family head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:37.06,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,As the replacement for our father, who was supposedly assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.60,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,There's no way the other people in the family would accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.10,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,You should do it, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:47.54,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,I'm the son of his mistress, and can't use the power of the Hyper Adapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.62,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,So I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:53.74,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,But you have what it takes to be the legitimate successor, both in terms of lineage and ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:59.42,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,You're going to help me out, especially to convince those annoying old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.74,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,You really think I'll agree to something like that-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.10,Default,Yaza,0,0,0,,Of course, you are free to abandon your inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.52,Default,Yaza,0,0,0,,If you do that, you can probably avoid being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:12.68,Default,Yaza,0,0,0,,But you'll also lose the chance to save your childhood friend, the Priestess of Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:13.84,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Asagi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.04,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,Right now, we still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:19.22,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,If you agree to help us, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.60,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,"Us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Have you finished talking to your guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.20,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:33.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I have a debt to pay to your father and the current board members of the Island Administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:38.02,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,If you're worried about your future, I might be willing to hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:49.82,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,The fact that I received this means... Yukina and I are once again roommates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:54.16,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,It means that the Lion King Organization officially accepted that we can live together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:00.88,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,I don't like that Akatsuki Kojou lives next door, but oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:04.18,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,If it's something like waking him up when he oversleeps or eating together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.08,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,I don't mind doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.14,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Sorry Yukina, but I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.32,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,This pisses me off for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.20,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Stupid Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.42,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.22,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,A preliminary test kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.86,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Yukina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.96,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A permit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:51.06,Default,soldier,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sorry, but you need a permit from the\NMan-made Island Administration to go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:56.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I just want to visit Asagi- I mean, one of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why would I need a permit for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.48,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll come back some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.54,Default,soldier,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,This is starting to get shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.34,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.66,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You don't look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.34,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.70,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's been getting a little cold lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Cold...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.34,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Himeragi, did you eat properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.14,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Let's go to a restaurant somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.56,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.96,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're definitely not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.76,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You should probably go home for a bit-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:49.86,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Please step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,This is a barrier that keeps people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:55.76,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:59.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, be careful. That person is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.08,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Sekkarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.26,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:19.64,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I, Sword Shaman of the High God and priestess of the Lion, beseech thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:20.38,Default,shike,0,0,0,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.66,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.32,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,The Spirit Bow technique... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:38.40,Default,shike,0,0,0,,I need you to calm down for a while, Fourth Primogenitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.82,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Sen...pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Sen...pai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.46,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, Himeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.14,Default,shike,0,0,0,,My word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:26.18,Default,shike,0,0,0,,I had an inkling ever since I heard that you used\NDivine Possession against Minamiya Natsuki, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:31.42,Default,shike,0,0,0,,That power... So it was like that after all, Yukina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:32.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Shike-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.60,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Wait... Shike-sama? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:42.16,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you're the real Nyanko-sensei!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.66,Default,Shike,0,0,0,,It's not like you were unaware of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.18,Default,Shike,0,0,0,,Now then, what should we do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:53.08,Default,Shike,0,0,0,,Now that I have seen it with my own eyes, I can't just let this pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, Shike-sama! I can still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:58.36,Default,Shike,0,0,0,,Yukina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hang on, you two! What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.70,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,We're running away, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Boundary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.52,Default,Shike,0,0,0,,Yukina... You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:24.96,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.30,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,One moment, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.50,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Wait... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:32.12,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ah, you're Yukina-chan's senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:35.68,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Hello. Umm... Is Akatsuki Kojou here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:40.98,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Umm... He said that he would visit Yazecchi... one of his friends in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.88,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,so he's not home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.82,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,So Yukina should be with him as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:45.90,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.88,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Umm... You're Yukina's classmate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.38,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,How has she been, recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.30,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Has she been acting differently in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.36,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.18,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ah, I think she hasn't had much of an appetite lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.82,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,She didn't eat much last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:06.66,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Also, she said she felt nauseous and only drank Lemon Squash for lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.40,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.06,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Akatsuki Kojou, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.84,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,What have you done to my Yukina!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.96,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Did Kojou-kun do something to Yukina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.66,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,I have no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.78,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,I need to find Yukina right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.04,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Thank you. Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.30,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ah, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.18,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.02,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,A test kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.64,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Wait... It's positive!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:58.64,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I had no idea that Nyanko-sensei was actually such a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.84,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why did she attack you, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:05.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Don't you think it was a little over the top for just testing a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:09.18,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I think Shike-sama was trying to drive me into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.16,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,She wanted to push me to the brink...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.38,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,To make you fight seriously, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Any reason why she had to go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.16,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.90,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Anyway, Himeragi, do you feel cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.64,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,If it keeps raining for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.76,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,H-Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:36.86,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.96,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I don't want to go home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:41.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Wait, what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.34,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's... That's a strange way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.88,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Besides, you live alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:52.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That house belongs to the Lion King Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:57.04,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Since I disobeyed Shike-sama, I'm sure it has been occupied by pursuers already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:01.08,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Ah... So that's what you meant by not wanting to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.58,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,But why is the Lion King Organization after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:10.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I know why they think that I am dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.36,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Sorry, I said something selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.78,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Senpai, please go home without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Without you... What are you planning to do, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I can't go back to that house anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:32.18,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But don't worry, I'm still keeping an eye on you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.28,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'll keep watching over you, until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.66,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:38.84,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:43.04,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh well, we don't have school tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.96,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Want to go for some karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.98,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.44,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You don't know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:54.34,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Of course I do! I've gone twice, with Nagisa-chan and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.38,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's good. Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:05.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Umm... I don't know any of the popular songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:08.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,And I can't sing like Aiba-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:13.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I didn't meant to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.36,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing for that, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,And besides, the one doing the singing is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The real one is apparently terrible at singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.46,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.54,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Alright then, we're going to karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.14,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,But how about we eat some ramen first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,After all that happened, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:36.06,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,That's right... If it's noodles, I might be able to eat it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's decided, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:41.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Asagi told me about a good shop that's not too far from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.04,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's called... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Itogami Noodle House.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.02,Default,clerk,0,0,0,,Two people, yes? Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.28,Default,clerk,0,0,0,,Would you mind sharing a table with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,We don't really mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:55.16,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,There seem to be a bunch of people waiting in line ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:59.04,Default,clerk,0,0,0,,About that... they refused to share a table, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.98,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Boyfriend-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.10,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,If it isn't Boyfriend-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.42,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,You are Empress-dono's boyfriend, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.92,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,This one is called Lydianne Didier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.72,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Do you not remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.90,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Ah! You're Asagi's friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.30,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,This one is vexed, Boyfriend-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:21.10,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Due to this one's lack of strength, Empress-dono is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.08,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,There is no choice but to rip through this abdomen of mine-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:24.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.08,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:30.22,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Do not stop me, Boyfriend-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:28.96,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let go, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.84,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can't do that with chopsticks anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.66,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,No matter how far Lydianne has fallen, she is still a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.74,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,Stop making such a racket, you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.10,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,You're being rude to the owner of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.54,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,If you wish to consume ramen, then sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.36,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,If not, then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,T-That's right. My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:45.60,Default,clerk,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.76,Default,clerk,0,0,0,,Here's your Itogami pork and seafood ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:03.90,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:09.44,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,A soup made from fresh seafood, pork, and vegetables that cannot be recreated anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:12.48,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,The noodles are on the thick side, made by the chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.74,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,I see originality in the ingredients as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.70,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,I see. No wonder Asagi recommended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.78,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.26,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Are you one of Asagi's gourmet friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.84,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, be careful what you say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:28.58,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,This person... is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:29.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No. But this person's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It might equal or even surpass that of Lord Ardeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:37.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But there is something strange about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:39.62,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,Know your place, Sword Shaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:44.68,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,I am interacting with the Fourth Primogenitor as a Prince of the Dynasty of Destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.00,Default,Ibliss,0,0,0,,A mere observer has no right to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A prince? And the Dynasty of Destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.66,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,His Highness, Ibriss-Bel Aziz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:54.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.84,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Wait, why is the Second Primogenitor's son here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:02.26,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,eating pork ramen on Itogami Island with Asagi's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.94,Default,Ibriss,0,0,0,,It's a pork and seafood ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:05.90,Default,Ibriss,0,0,0,,Don't get it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:10.96,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,This esteemed person saved this one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:11.96,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:19.16,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Just earlier, this one attempted to infiltrate Keystone Gate together with Hizamaru, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.94,Default,computer,0,0,0,,Warning. Received damage from an anti-material rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.56,Default,computer,0,0,0,,Close-range damage from a small bore Gatling gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.64,Default,computer,0,0,0,,Heavy damage to the front left leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.84,Default,computer,0,0,0,,Release lock from joint #4.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:51.48,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Are they not... regular people!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.78,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Are they the Island Guard's SSG!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:56.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,SSG?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:58.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,A strike force comprised of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:03.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It is an unofficial special force, supposedly reporting directly to the Board of Directors of the Island Administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:09.14,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,And so, the deteriorating situation forced this one to cede ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:10.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You retreated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:22.48,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Launch the wire anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:24.52,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Aim for the monorail bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.36,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,A close escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:39.46,Default,computer,0,0,0,,Wire anchor unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:42.40,Default,computer,0,0,0,,Heavy damage to the rear legs and main power unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:46.02,Default,computer,0,0,0,,Switching life-support systems to backup power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.72,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Is this the end of the road...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.52,Default,Ibriss,0,0,0,,Worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:05.66,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,It cannot be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.48,0:23:12.76,Default,Ibriss,0,0,0,,I was reluctant, but she is an acquaintance of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:17.33,Default,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,516)}Thank you for\Nfinishing your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:15.40,Default,Ibriss,0,0,0,,I ended up bringing her under my protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:17.18,Default,Ibriss,0,0,0,,It was merely a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:19.26,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I understand what happened, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:23.26,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why did you try and sneak into such a dangerous place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.78,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Is it not obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:30.88,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,It was to save Empress-dono, who has been confined by the Island Administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:33.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Confined!? The Island Administration has Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.10,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,On the deepest level of the Keystone Gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:40.34,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Therein lies the impregnable Floor Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:44.70,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,In the center of that area lies Cain's Coffin, also called "C".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:49.84,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Empress-dono has been imprisoned there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:57.24,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.94,0:23:58.90,Default,Didier,0,0,0,,Kojou...
